---
layout: base.njk
isHomepage: true
needsLeaflet: true
---

{# Hero #}
<div class="hero">
    <img src="/assets/hero-wafer.jpg" alt="Chip dies on a wafer" class="hero-wafer">
    <div class="date-badge">{{ site.event_date_display | upper }} &middot; DTU LYNGBY</div>
    <h1>DTU <span>Chip</span>day {{ site.event_year }}</h1>
    <p>A half-day conference and exhibition for students, faculty, and industry professionals to explore and develop the Danish chip design ecosystem.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
        <a class="cta cta-secondary" href="#program">Program</a>
        <a class="cta" href="https://www.conferencemanager.dk/dtuchipday14042026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Register Now</a>
    </div>
    <div class="countdown" id="countdown">
        <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-days">--</span><span class="label">Days</span></div>
        <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-hours">--</span><span class="label">Hours</span></div>
        <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-mins">--</span><span class="label">Minutes</span></div>
        <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-secs">--</span><span class="label">Seconds</span></div>
    </div>
</div>

{# Sponsors & Exhibitors #}
{% set sponsors = companies | selectattr("sponsor") %}
{% if sponsors | length %}
<section id="sponsors">
    <h2>Sponsors &amp; Exhibitors</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Companies with a stand at DTU Chipday {{ site.event_year }}</p>
    <div class="sponsors-grid">
        {% for c in sponsors %}
        <a href="{{ c.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="sponsor-badge">{{ c.name }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">
{% endif %}

{# Program #}
<section id="program">
    <h2>Program</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">DTU Chip Day {{ site.event_year }} &mdash; {{ site.event_date_display }}</p>

    {% for item in program2026 %}
    {% include "partials/program-item.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
</section>

<hr class="divider">

{# About #}
<section id="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">What is DTU Chip Day?</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
            <h3>The Event</h3>
            <p>DTU Chip Day is a yearly half-day conference and exhibition initiated in 2022 as a post-corona initiative by DTU Compute and a group of industry players who wanted to highlight the important but often overlooked Danish semiconductor industry. Each year in early January, a small organizing team from academia and industry come together to plan the event, held every spring at DTU.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
            <h3>Danish Chip Design</h3>
            <p>Denmark has a world-class chip design ecosystem spanning global companies with large design teams, specialized SMEs, and cutting-edge university research. From hearing aids to quantum cryptography, Danish engineers deliver silicon expertise across a wide range of domains. Chip Day brings this community together &mdash; big and small &mdash; to connect, share knowledge, and inspire the next generation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
            <h3>Who Should Attend</h3>
            <p>Students, faculty, and industry professionals interested in the Danish chip design ecosystem. Expect exciting talks, company exhibitions, networking, and opportunities for thesis projects and positions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Contact Organizing Team</h3>
    <div class="companies-grid" style="max-width: 700px;">
        {% for org in organizers %}
        <div class="about-card">
            <h3>{{ org.name }}</h3>
            <p>{{ org.role }}<br>
            <a href="mailto:{{ org.email }}">{{ org.email }}</a>
            {% if org.phone %}<br><a href="tel:{{ org.phone }}">{{ org.phone }}</a>{% endif %}
            </p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

{# Venue #}
<section id="venue">
    <h2>Venue</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">{{ site.venue }}</p>
    <div id="map"></div>
</section>

